00:00:03.405 --> 00:00:08.715
So, today is the second day of Navaratri.

00:00:10.882 --> 00:00:16.595
I told you yesterday that first the auspiciousness

00:00:16.816 --> 00:00:23.788
and the holiness was created through the creation of Shri Ganesha.

00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:29.448
So that this world is fulfilled with auspiciousness and holiness.

00:00:30.250 --> 00:00:32.550
We can see in the history

00:00:33.077 --> 00:00:38.136
that people in the olden times cared for auspiciousness

00:00:38.664 --> 00:00:42.706
and were afraid of God, they had fear for God

00:00:43.097 --> 00:00:46.140
and they didn’t challenge God at all.

00:00:49.425 --> 00:00:55.558
But gradually, the evil took over

00:00:56.730 --> 00:01:03.741
and so this auspiciousness and holiness started

00:01:04.621 --> 00:01:07.644
getting – not exhausted – but sleeping off.

00:01:08.049 --> 00:01:13.220
So Ganesha started sleeping, and as Ganesha sleeps

00:01:13.982 --> 00:01:17.556
the people are not afraid of God.

00:01:18.211 --> 00:01:20.993
They think they can do what they like:

00:01:21.521 --> 00:01:27.380
what can God do, after all, who is He? We don’t see it.

00:01:28.747 --> 00:01:33.396
They also have no gratitude for what God has done for you.

00:01:34.138 --> 00:01:42.126
They have no gratitude about the blessings of this universe

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:50.115
that he was created, all the beauty that God gave you

00:01:50.798 --> 00:01:56.868
because they’re ignorant and in ignorance they forget everything.

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:06.599
Now the problem started more when Ganesha started sleeping.

00:02:07.556 --> 00:02:11.892
With his power, people were afraid of God, they were righteous,

00:02:12.302 --> 00:02:17.302
they wanted to be good people, they didn’t want to commit sins,

00:02:17.791 --> 00:02:20.798
they didn’t want to do wrong things,

00:02:21.130 --> 00:02:24.539
they wanted to keep their attention clean

00:02:24.845 --> 00:02:27.371
and put attention to good things.

00:02:27.606 --> 00:02:32.527
Such people existed because you can see the temples,

00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:35.042
the big churches,

00:02:35.336 --> 00:02:39.398
the big mosques that were built in the name of God.

00:02:40.125 --> 00:02:43.441
And they didn’t have so much money, nothing

00:02:43.696 --> 00:02:46.229
but just out of devotion they did it.

00:02:46.664 --> 00:02:48.664
So, they had devotion for God.

00:02:49.164 --> 00:02:56.308
Another side was that people like we can say, the people

00:02:57.442 --> 00:03:03.047
who were searching God were trying to find out the ways and methods

00:03:03.242 --> 00:03:11.829
how they could reach God and there was such a big search.

00:03:13.021 --> 00:03:16.923
They didn’t want material things, they didn’t care for it.

00:03:17.099 --> 00:03:22.880
I mean, for them, it was too low to think of it.

00:03:24.497 --> 00:03:27.855
But gradually so, it happened

00:03:29.073 --> 00:03:35.014
that these simple needs of life became very complicated,

00:03:36.303 --> 00:03:49.683
then first they had started to fight with each other.

00:03:51.551 --> 00:03:56.939
And then when they fight with each other it was out of selfishness,

00:03:57.426 --> 00:04:03.136
it was all kind of uncollective temperament that they developed

00:04:03.941 --> 00:04:08.079
may be food, maybe some material thing,

00:04:08.477 --> 00:04:12.242
all these things started crawling up into their ignorance.

00:04:12.820 --> 00:04:16.459
As a result, they became very blind

00:04:17.365 --> 00:04:27.047
and gradually they became sub-human, barbaric.

00:04:29.373 --> 00:04:33.607
So, the second phase started where

00:04:33.959 --> 00:04:38.665
just after the vegetation and everything was created,

00:04:39.994 --> 00:04:45.521
the fire of the Mother Earth started coming out as an anger

00:04:47.096 --> 00:04:52.200
for these animals that they grew up,

00:04:52.572 --> 00:05:01.200
also were very-very dangerous type and were troublesome,

00:05:01.727 --> 00:05:04.340
who were in the evolutionary process

00:05:04.398 --> 00:05:07.504
were very-very big sized very big sized things,

00:05:08.076 --> 00:05:14.790
but not intelligent. Extremely cruel and big sized animals.

00:05:15.416 --> 00:05:19.904
All these evolutionary processes start but before that,

00:05:20.509 --> 00:05:32.872
only the Mother Earth’s fire started burning the stone inside.

00:05:33.654 --> 00:05:38.380
Because as I told you first it was taken nearer the Sun,

00:05:38.478 --> 00:05:41.251
this Mother Earth, and then towards the Moon.

00:05:41.428 --> 00:05:44.021
So that the upper crust, though it was

00:05:44.119 --> 00:05:47.361
it had become cooled down and it had formed ice

00:05:47.514 --> 00:05:52.786
and then it melted away into the water, still the inside,

00:05:53.573 --> 00:05:58.274
inside the ocean, the Mother Earth was very hot.

00:05:58.934 --> 00:06:01.665
And that She started coming out.

00:06:02.162 --> 00:06:05.402
And when this heat started coming it burned

00:06:05.565 --> 00:06:09.289
many trees and many stones,

00:06:09.569 --> 00:06:13.423
with that burning, carbon was formed.

00:06:14.317 --> 00:06:20.580
Now, this carbon started absorbing

00:06:22.807 --> 00:06:25.945
all the gazes that were outside

00:06:26.286 --> 00:06:31.101
and purifying the atmosphere quite a lot.

00:06:31.935 --> 00:06:36.989
Plus, this carbon is the basis of our organic chemistry.

00:06:37.367 --> 00:06:40.426
So first the in-organic chemistry was there

00:06:40.713 --> 00:06:43.723
in the sense chemicals were produced

00:06:43.815 --> 00:06:48.804
and then with the carbon started the organic chemistry

00:06:49.227 --> 00:06:53.283
and that’s the beginning of life we should say

00:06:54.397 --> 00:06:58.908
because then nitrogen it started absorbing

00:06:59.749 --> 00:07:03.400
and they formed amino acids.

00:07:03.913 --> 00:07:07.580
These amino acids are the basis of life.

00:07:08.206 --> 00:07:10.959
So that is how the life started.

00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:14.904
But the first life grew in the water

00:07:15.138 --> 00:07:19.103
and you know the whole evolutionary process how it took place

00:07:19.376 --> 00:07:22.400
in the second centre, Swadhisthana

00:07:22.615 --> 00:07:26.326
which had created all the universes and all that,

00:07:27.131 --> 00:07:34.529
all around in the Mother Earth there was water and

00:07:36.033 --> 00:07:40.330
on that surface of Mother Earth life started growing

00:07:40.526 --> 00:07:42.572
then the evolutionary took place.

00:07:42.644 --> 00:07:46.146
Evolutionary process took place in this Bhavasagara,

00:07:47.436 --> 00:07:51.146
till we come to the human stage as I told you

00:07:51.304 --> 00:07:53.861
there were animals first who came up

00:07:53.959 --> 00:07:56.654
in the evolutionary process,

00:07:56.776 --> 00:07:59.971
they grew up and they grew

00:08:00.124 --> 00:08:03.315
very big then they had to become small,

00:08:03.569 --> 00:08:05.628
then they became very cunning,

00:08:05.706 --> 00:08:08.362
all kinds of things happened in the evolutionary process,

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:10.315
left and right, right and left.

00:08:10.374 --> 00:08:13.147
Ultimately a human being was created

00:08:13.593 --> 00:08:18.061
He too was in the image – not of God at that time,

00:08:18.101 --> 00:08:24.526
but in the image of an animal because the animal has – hum,

00:08:27.339 --> 00:08:30.659
he has come from the animal stage,

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:37.827
but God created later man into the image of Himself

00:08:38.023 --> 00:08:43.999
in the sense is, out of these barbaric models –

00:08:44.195 --> 00:08:48.097
we call them we call them half-man, half-this thing,

00:08:48.214 --> 00:08:52.374
like you can say the monkeys becoming man.

00:08:52.486 --> 00:08:55.334
Then He created something –

00:08:55.769 --> 00:09:01.252
you can call it as Adam and Eve before, two models.

00:09:02.073 --> 00:09:06.077
So this was all done at that time,

00:09:06.448 --> 00:09:10.549
as you know that Adam and Eve are symbolic

00:09:10.862 --> 00:09:19.413
two personalities who wanted to know what is good and what is bad.

00:09:20.393 --> 00:09:24.413
And because of this urge to find out,

00:09:24.609 --> 00:09:27.749
that we can find, we can,

00:09:28.231 --> 00:09:32.922
also in the search of God many people think there’s no need to have

00:09:33.136 --> 00:09:37.394
any advice from any Realized soul,

00:09:37.641 --> 00:09:41.113
we can do it ourselves, what is the need

00:09:41.366 --> 00:09:45.468
to have Mother to tell us anything, we can do it ourselves.

00:09:45.757 --> 00:09:48.920
So they wanted to keep themselves on their own.

00:09:49.214 --> 00:09:51.881
So God said: “All right, you go ahead.”

00:09:52.241 --> 00:09:55.600
And that’s how the circle started

00:09:55.757 --> 00:09:58.882
in the search of the truth. And as you know

00:09:59.131 --> 00:10:03.030
we are here today enlightened.

00:10:04.038 --> 00:10:07.866
So then enlightenment has come to you,

00:10:09.058 --> 00:10:13.233
ultimately, but one had to go through

00:10:13.409 --> 00:10:20.147
the desert, the darkness of ignorance and then come to this stage.

00:10:21.183 --> 00:10:25.909
Then the state came in that we needed somebody to lead us,

00:10:26.070 --> 00:10:33.683
as somebody’s needed in the process of you can call it the

00:10:35.267 --> 00:10:47.550
evolution, one fish came out and crawled and became a reptile,

00:10:48.761 --> 00:10:53.936
in the same way, you needed every time some leader to come out

00:10:54.249 --> 00:10:57.604
to raise you higher and higher and higher.

00:10:57.819 --> 00:11:02.444
So the first incarnation, I would say, was that of the Goddess.

00:11:02.874 --> 00:11:08.870
She was the first who came to lead people towards God.

00:11:09.163 --> 00:11:19.413
Because if you see in the Void, we have this chakra of Swadhistana

00:11:20.194 --> 00:11:26.854
and we have also the great Gurus, prophets who came

00:11:27.402 --> 00:11:32.967
to try to save human beings. But this was later.

00:11:33.417 --> 00:11:39.999
Before came the Goddess, to save people from

00:11:40.331 --> 00:11:47.967
all these ways of destruction.

00:11:48.280 --> 00:11:51.674
Some had become very evil

00:11:51.734 --> 00:11:55.131
people who were called as Rakshasas, devils

00:11:55.855 --> 00:12:00.796
and some were, had become good people.

00:12:02.456 --> 00:12:08.389
Out of them then the Goddess created these great saints,

00:12:08.546 --> 00:12:10.846
they worshipped the Mother and they become

00:12:10.963 --> 00:12:14.869
great saints then became incarnations of saintliness.

00:12:15.314 --> 00:12:20.021
So the first incarnation that ever came was that of the Goddess.

00:12:20.744 --> 00:12:27.107
And we see, on the second Yuga that we can call, She came.

00:12:27.322 --> 00:12:33.240
She came before Shri Krishna, She came before Shri Rama

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:41.619
and She saved people from getting drowned into Bhavasagara.

00:12:43.104 --> 00:12:48.748
This then created great saints and sages and Gurus

00:12:49.744 --> 00:12:53.357
who tried to save people.

00:12:53.865 --> 00:12:58.963
We have Gurus who were very great,

00:13:00.565 --> 00:13:03.591
I should say saints and very evolved,

00:13:03.865 --> 00:13:06.673
but also we had some who were right-sided,

00:13:06.908 --> 00:13:09.408
who knew all kinds of

00:13:09.565 --> 00:13:14.170
Vedas, they knew all kinds of sciences, they knew all kinds of

00:13:15.345 --> 00:13:19.912
– you can call them the divine weapons and things like that.

00:13:20.518 --> 00:13:23.228
And we also had left-sided

00:13:23.424 --> 00:13:27.287
Gurus who believed in the devotion,

00:13:28.973 --> 00:13:35.434
like you can say Moses was there, Abraham, Moses all these,

00:13:35.708 --> 00:13:40.941
people came who were left-sided, Muhammad was there,

00:13:41.157 --> 00:13:45.410
one of the last ones you can say and then Nanaka [Sainath].

00:13:46.182 --> 00:13:51.328
So came the devotion to God, devotion to the

00:13:52.213 --> 00:13:55.725
All-pervading Power started like this.

00:13:56.702 --> 00:14:03.928
So in this stage, that people tried to murder these

00:14:04.573 --> 00:14:07.088
great saints like Socrates, like

00:14:07.206 --> 00:14:09.822
we know everybody had to suffer so much

00:14:10.392 --> 00:14:12.673
because nobody

00:14:13.454 --> 00:14:18.278
in the collective liked saints or goodness or righteousness.

00:14:18.591 --> 00:14:21.122
That’s how we had fallen down so much

00:14:21.169 --> 00:14:23.466
at the time as you on the time

