00:21:06.365 --> 00:21:08.038
They’ll not put oil.

00:21:08.429 --> 00:21:11.827
Because nobody puts oil so they’re not putting oil in their heads.

00:21:11.968 --> 00:21:13.460
Then they’ll become bald-headed,

00:21:13.546 --> 00:21:16.374
they come to me: “Mother we’ve lost our hair”.

00:21:16.475 --> 00:21:18.905
You put on oil! I’ve told you to put on oil.

00:21:19.304 --> 00:21:21.975
Why don’t you put on oil? They won’t just do anything

00:21:22.124 --> 00:21:25.428
because the rest of the people don’t put on oil, we should not put.

00:21:25.820 --> 00:21:29.124
You are not them; you are different. Try to understand

00:21:29.187 --> 00:21:32.960
you are not the other people. You are the leaders

00:21:33.999 --> 00:21:36.857
and you shouldn’t follow them, they should follow you.

00:21:41.499 --> 00:21:44.694
Instead of that, you are following all

00:21:45.304 --> 00:21:50.155
the general opinion of the people and you want to live like them,

00:21:50.321 --> 00:21:52.219
then how can you be a saint?

00:21:52.279 --> 00:21:56.966
A saint lives like the way
he has to live because he has the wisdom.

00:22:02.490 --> 00:22:05.052
And that is what you have to understand,

00:22:05.248 --> 00:22:07.880
that all these ideas have gone into your head

00:22:07.979 --> 00:22:10.435
and it’s a very dedicate operation for Me.

00:22:11.423 --> 00:22:12.930
Even to tell you something.

00:22:12.962 --> 00:22:15.579
If I tell something to the ladies they’ll start crying.

00:22:16.490 --> 00:22:19.459
If I tell something to men, they’ll leave Sahaja Yoga

00:22:20.201 --> 00:22:22.748
as if they’re obliging Me, is wrong.

00:22:23.186 --> 00:22:25.888
What you have to do is that God has chosen you

00:22:25.967 --> 00:22:27.638
to be the leaders of the people.

00:22:27.772 --> 00:22:31.334
To be the leaders. Do you know you are going to be the leaders?

00:22:33.232 --> 00:22:35.099
And then how a leader should be?

00:22:35.287 --> 00:22:36.967
It should be a model.

00:22:39.586 --> 00:22:42.157
And that’s why in the Islam

00:22:42.194 --> 00:22:45.407
or in Nanaka, praises complete surrender.

00:22:45.583 --> 00:22:47.935
What you surrender is nothing but this Ego and these

00:22:47.989 --> 00:22:50.177
conditionings, these nonsensical ideas.

00:22:51.037 --> 00:22:53.036
And that you have to surrender.

00:22:53.355 --> 00:22:55.589
That’s very important and surprisingly

00:22:55.745 --> 00:22:57.682
how Mohammad has said

00:22:57.769 --> 00:22:59.478
that Islam is to surrender,

00:22:59.572 --> 00:23:01.728
must be the reason he must be knowing

00:23:01.917 --> 00:23:06.328
that now ego is going to overpower the left side.

00:23:13.330 --> 00:23:15.291
We are not ordinary people.

00:23:15.892 --> 00:23:18.774
How many people know how to raise Kundalini?

00:23:19.805 --> 00:23:24.730
But still, I see people do not know on the feet where is the,

00:23:25.481 --> 00:23:27.433
where are the chakras are there.

00:23:27.707 --> 00:23:29.949
Simple, simple things they don’t know.

00:23:31.316 --> 00:23:32.855
I don’t know what time,

00:23:32.926 --> 00:23:35.355
where they spend their time, what do they talk.

00:23:35.715 --> 00:23:38.691
The other day I asked these Indian girls what are the

00:23:39.136 --> 00:23:41.590
stones that are for all these.

00:23:41.809 --> 00:23:44.808
They didn’t know, I ‘m surprised, none of them knew.

00:23:46.762 --> 00:23:49.605
They’re Indians, I mean, I thought they should know all that.

00:23:49.699 --> 00:23:50.754
It’s all there,

00:23:50.894 --> 00:23:52.972
but they don’t know that. I don’t know what,

00:23:53.032 --> 00:23:55.964
morning till evening they’re talking but what do they talk?

00:23:56.371 --> 00:23:57.816
You should find out.

00:23:58.745 --> 00:24:02.862
It’s all I’ve said it, it’s all in the – in what you call this

00:24:04.674 --> 00:24:08.271
– on the tape, finished. That’s all.

00:24:09.216 --> 00:24:11.590
This knowledge should be in your brain

00:24:11.965 --> 00:24:14.841
and the vibrations should be in your hearts.

00:24:16.378 --> 00:24:18.557
So, Navaratri is a big preparation.

00:24:18.925 --> 00:24:20.830
We have to know that

00:24:21.776 --> 00:24:24.346
the knowledge of Sahaja Yoga has to come into us,

00:24:24.409 --> 00:24:27.955
otherwise, why will people ask- think that you are saints?

00:24:29.961 --> 00:24:32.148
Nobody’s going to believe it

00:24:32.719 --> 00:24:34.226
that you are saints,

00:24:34.674 --> 00:24:37.245
in your behaviour, in your knowledge,

00:24:37.745 --> 00:24:39.939
in your dealing with others.

00:24:40.214 --> 00:24:44.050
In everything a Sahaja Yogi should be something outstanding.

00:24:44.925 --> 00:24:45.956
When I said,

00:24:46.094 --> 00:24:49.596
“You have become, you all have to become your own masters”.

00:24:50.034 --> 00:24:51.705
Then they use it the other way round.

00:24:51.870 --> 00:24:54.604
They tell the leader: “Now we have become our own masters”.

00:24:54.703 --> 00:24:56.063
It’s not the way.

00:24:57.646 --> 00:24:59.507
So, the first thing is wisdom,

00:25:00.367 --> 00:25:03.358
wisdom to understand that we are Sahaja Yogis.

00:25:03.507 --> 00:25:05.030
Assume the power.

00:25:05.398 --> 00:25:08.202
Sometimes I feel as if a

00:25:08.499 --> 00:25:11.562
beggar is made a king supposing;

00:25:12.601 --> 00:25:14.796
still he doesn’t assume his position.

00:25:15.014 --> 00:25:18.437
Anybody coming he says, “Can you give me one penny?”

00:25:18.914 --> 00:25:20.514
Though he’s a king.

00:25:22.584 --> 00:25:24.490
Something like that.

00:25:25.195 --> 00:25:28.484
Now you have to become the leaders of the world,

00:25:28.828 --> 00:25:30.500
all over the world

00:25:30.664 --> 00:25:32.984
and this is something to be assumed

00:25:33.125 --> 00:25:36.625
and felt. It’s not ego, it’s a reality.

00:25:38.344 --> 00:25:41.218
Because once you know that it is the reality

00:25:41.336 --> 00:25:43.164
you immediately change yourself.

00:25:43.399 --> 00:25:47.304
Immediately you will think that, “Now, what are we doing?

00:25:50.414 --> 00:25:52.015
How much do we know?

00:25:53.086 --> 00:25:56.234
We are the leaders, the responsibility’s ours”.

00:25:58.102 --> 00:26:02.187
If that is understood, you’ll be surprised that

00:26:03.578 --> 00:26:08.398
nothing is needed to work out your cleansing.

00:26:09.750 --> 00:26:11.882
Just automatically it will work,

00:26:12.055 --> 00:26:14.890
that’s My blessing to you. Accept it.

00:26:16.586 --> 00:26:18.630
But you must

00:26:18.865 --> 00:26:22.232
feel that, “I have to be all right”, you have to feel it.

00:26:23.834 --> 00:26:26.709
The situation becomes helpless for Me sometimes,

00:26:26.990 --> 00:26:29.611
if I tell something to somebody they’ll start crying

00:26:30.119 --> 00:26:32.205
or they’ll run away from Sahaja Yoga.

00:26:32.439 --> 00:26:33.626
So, what am I to do?

00:26:33.790 --> 00:26:36.462
Should I leave you at the same stage as it is?

00:26:36.797 --> 00:26:38.992
Now, to save you from evil

00:26:39.258 --> 00:26:41.383
is not the same as to fight

00:26:41.430 --> 00:26:44.359
Mahishasura or Narakasura, not that way.

00:26:44.828 --> 00:26:46.843
Because Narakasura is also gone into your head

00:26:46.906 --> 00:26:49.336
and Mahishasura is also gone into your head.

00:26:51.473 --> 00:26:54.089
So, the only thing one has to do is to understand, “There is

00:26:54.129 --> 00:26:58.128
this one in me, I ask that to get out”.

00:26:59.215 --> 00:27:01.128
Once you work it out that way,

00:27:01.181 --> 00:27:03.683
you are doing Navaratri itself.

00:27:04.285 --> 00:27:05.480
You have got powers,

00:27:05.566 --> 00:27:08.839
you have the knowledge, you know you can feel it.

00:27:09.098 --> 00:27:11.019
Just take out all these conditionings:

00:27:11.270 --> 00:27:13.183
we are something different.

00:27:16.371 --> 00:27:18.332
You are not ordinary people.

00:27:22.793 --> 00:27:24.855
You are something very special.

00:27:25.937 --> 00:27:28.827
And why should we, at all,

00:27:29.062 --> 00:27:30.320
behave like others

00:27:30.406 --> 00:27:33.148
or like the way others behave? You’re not like others.

00:27:34.351 --> 00:27:37.562
And what a big thing you have, what a big knowledge you have!

00:27:37.922 --> 00:27:40.093
Look at Christ, He was alone.

00:27:40.828 --> 00:27:44.038
He talked about what he wanted to say to multitudes, he talked.

00:27:44.429 --> 00:27:46.703
He was crucified, still, He talked.

00:27:48.086 --> 00:27:50.077
Till the end.

00:27:50.773 --> 00:27:54.746
But He was knowledgeable

00:27:56.153 --> 00:27:59.433
and you might say that Mother he was an incarnation, all right.

00:28:00.425 --> 00:28:02.051
But in no way you are less now:

00:28:02.080 --> 00:28:05.074
you know how to raise the Kundalini, you know everything.

00:28:06.176 --> 00:28:07.776
You are my children.

00:28:10.598 --> 00:28:12.566
So, I would suggest that

00:28:12.778 --> 00:28:15.082
to develop wisdom, you must meditate

00:28:15.192 --> 00:28:16.801
and be in the centre,

00:28:17.284 --> 00:28:18.761
so all these things will go away:

00:28:18.848 --> 00:28:21.418
just be away from this nonsense.

00:28:21.551 --> 00:28:27.202
In what atmosphere we live, what we do, it’s not important.

00:28:29.913 --> 00:28:34.381
We have to know that we are something exceptional.

00:28:35.054 --> 00:28:39.553
All the Ganas, all the angels are just waiting- [end of recording].
